                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " THE CL-36 TRANSITIONS WERE",
                " USED AS A STANDARD FOR BOTH ENERGY AND EFFICIENCY.",
                " THEY WERE OBTAINED BY ADDING 200 MG OF NACL TO THE",
                " SAMPLE AND IRRADIATING DURING DAYS 170 - 177, AND THEN",
                " MEASURING FOR 21 HOURS."
              ]
            }
          ],
